For each iteration formula_17, let formula_18 be the quotient extracted so far, formula_19 be the intermediate dividend, formula_20 be the intermediate remainder, formula_21 be the next digit of the original dividend, and formula_22 be the next digit of the quotient. By definition of digits in base formula_23, formula_24. All values are natural numbers. We initiate 
